3.36.0 – March 9, 2020
============================

Here is a new stable release! This cycle has seen two
bugs fixed, that were making the moves counting fail.

Translations updated (since 3.35.91):
  Catalan: Jordi Mas
  Croatian: Goran Vidović
  Czech: Marek Černocký (help)
  Danish: Alan Mortensen
