  Indonesian: Kukuh Syafaat
  Italian: Milo Casagrande
  Korean: Seong-ho Cho
  Polish: Piotr Drąg
  Slovenian: Matej Urbančič
  Swedish: Anders Jonsson

3.35.91 - February 15, 2020
============================

Many code improvements and cleanings, so please test.
Two bugs have been fixed in the moves counting; also,
unmovable tiles will not be selected anymore when the
player is dropping a tile, and it should feel better.

Translations updated:
  Basque: Asier Sarasua Garmendia
  Croatian: Goran Vidović
  Czech: Marek Černocký
